🧮 Simple Calculator (Python CLI)
A basic command-line calculator built using Python. This program allows users to perform simple arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

Features
  Addition  
  Subtraction  
  Multiplication  
  Division  
  Handles division by zero  
  Handles invalid input choices  

How It Works
 Enter the first number
 Enter the second number
 Choose an operation:
 1 → Addition
 2 → Subtraction
 3 → Multiplication
 4 → Division
 The program displays the result
